premise_source_doc_sentence: The first credited guest star was actor Sam McMurray who appeared in `` Homer 's Odyssey '' , the show 's third episode .
Sometimes an actor might not be credited as guest star on his or her first appearance , but will be in subsequent episodes .
As of June 14 , 2010 , WWE decided to slowly phase out the guest star concept on Raw , by only scheduling guest stars every other week , with the possibility of having a guest star only when needed .

While a lot of these guest appearances are for fictional roles , a large number of the guest stars on the show are celebrities playing themselves  (  or fictionalized versions thereof  )  , including actors , comedians and sportspeople .
The first episode that featured guest stars was `` The Little Guy '' , the show 's second episode , which garnered ten guest appearances .
